RI Coverage
These charts list On-demand instances, and estimate potential saving from purchasing reservations for the minimum number running over the last 30 days.

sf_uiModel.markdownText:
RI Utilization
These charts identify reservations that have been purchased but are not being used, and estimate wasted cost based on the minimum unused reservations over 30 days.
